data.description:
A breathtaking residence in impeccable shape, situated at the center of Gold Canyon, providing incredible vistas of the majestic Superstition Mountains. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by recently installed luxury vinyl flooring and an expansive, welcoming entrance hall, graced by a sturdy 8-foot oak front door. The family room features a propane-gas fireplace, ideal for hosting intimate gatherings and making enduring memories with your close ones. On the lower level, there is also a formal dining room and a complete secondary suite with a private bathroom equipped with double sinks and a walk-in shower. This secluded sanctuary is ideal for accommodating guests or creating a comfortable space for extended family. The kitchen is well-appointed with granite countertops, double ovens, a breakfast bar, a reverse osmosis system, and a spacious walk-in pantry for all your kitchen essentials. Whether you're an aspiring chef or simply love to cook, this kitchen is designed to cater to your needs and enhance your culinary experience.

Moving to the upper level, you'll find an additional spacious family room and a generous loft area with a wet bar equipped with its own reverse osmosis system, creating an ideal space for entertainment and relaxation. A sizable and inviting deck offers stunning views of the Superstition Mountains, serving as a peaceful backdrop for your morning coffee or evening get-togethers.

The expansive primary suite on the upper level is a haven of comfort, featuring a roomy bathroom with double sinks complemented by granite counters and a large updated walk-in shower. This private sanctuary allows you to escape from the outside world and indulge in ultimate relaxation and rejuvenation.

Step out into the backyard oasis, which includes a propane-heated pebbletec pool with an enchanting water feature, a propane-heated spa, pavers, and a built-in BBQ. Recent upgrades in 2021, such as a new pool filter and pump, ensure you can enjoy and maintain the pool optimally.

The four-car garage is equipped with a car lift and garage cabinets, offering ample space for your vehicles and extra storage. The laundry room, complete with cabinets, ensures convenience and efficiency, making household chores a breeze.

This exceptional home comes with owned solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings, backed by a 25-year transferable warranty. Notable upgrades include two new Lennox HVAC systems installed in July 2022, Anderson windows added in 2020, fresh exterior paint, and new carpet in 2019. Fiberglass doors were installed in 2020, and a new foam roof was put in place in 2019. The Kinetico water softener, two reverse osmosis systems, and a water heater added in 2020 enhance your comfort and convenience. New laminate flooring downstairs comes with a 50-year transferrable warranty.

The laundry room with cabinets ensures convenience and practicality, making household chores a breeze. This exceptional home is equipped with owned solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings with a 25-year transferable warranty. The floorplan makes it easy to add a 4th and 5th bedroom to this magnificent home.
